Package ca.bc.gov.open.cpf.plugin.impl

Class BusinessApplicationPluginExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.bc.gov.open.cpf.plugin.impl.BusinessApplicationPluginExecutor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBusinessApplicationPluginExecutor, com.revolsys.io.BaseCloseable, Closeable, AutoCloseable
    public class BusinessApplicationPluginExecutor
extends Object
implements IBusinessApplicationPluginExecutor
    The BusinessApplicationPluginExecutor can be used to simulate running a BusinessApplicationPlugin with the CPF. This can be used to test the business application without deploying it to the CPF.

        public static IBusinessApplicationPluginExecutor getInstance()
        Get a proxy reference to the default executor. Make sure the instance is closed after use.

   executor.execute(parameters);
 }
